snippet.title: Help Me Now (Announcement trailer).
snippet.description: This game has been in development since october 2018. This game is based on survival horror, with puzzles and challenges for the player. You will have to deal with the intense suspense and horror of the game during gameplays. Lucas Lopes I am developing this game that will make you shiver!
